Example :
Set-Content reminder.txt -Value "social security numbers" -Stream secret.info - Secret into sec.info
Get-Content reminder.txt - outputs reminder.txt (Secret)
Get-Item reminder.txt -Stream * - View Stream (verbose)
Get-Item reminder.txt -Stream * | Select FileName,Stream - View Stream (not so verbose)
wscript .\text.txt:secret.vbs - execute ADS script
certutil -hashfile test.txt MD5 - Check hash

